description: Frozen treats and a funky good time are what you'll find when you visit Funky Monkeys Shaved Ice! When you need Wichita's finest frozen treats, then there's no one else who can quite beat this truck’s flavor, quality, and friendly service. With dozens of specialty shaved ice flavors to choose from, as well as some superb hot or iced coffee and delicious baked goods, Funky Monkeys Shaved Ice is sure to have something real yummy for you.
name: Funky Monkeys Shaved Ice
